description:
Interested in learning directly from Chick? Join the Chick Corea Academy today! Click here now: https://www.chickcoreaacademy.com/
 
Watch the announcement from the audience along with team Chick Corea http://chickcorea.com. Lenny White produced the Grammy-winning Corea, Clarke & White album "Forever". Chick took home the statue for Best Improvised Jazz Solo (for Forever's "500 Miles High") and the album won Best Jazz Instrumental Album. http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xTrdkqcC8jE
fulltitle: Chick Corea & Stanley Clarke Accept 2 Grammy Awards
